programs.title: George Town Heritage Celebrations 2023
programs.description: George Town Heritage Celebrations is an annual community-powered event that commemorates the inscription of George Town as a UNESCO World Heritage Site on 7 July 2008. It celebrates the living heritage of George Town – its multicultural practices, food, arts, and crafts, as well as cultural festivities that highlight the history and local cultural pride.
